'''BC Vytis''' is a professional team based in [[Šakiai]], [[Lithuania]] that currently plays in [[National Basketball League (Lithuania)|National Basketball League]]. In 2015, the club fans selected new club name and logo.

==Club achievements==
* 2013–14 season: [[National Basketball League (Lithuania)|NKL]] Round of 16
* 2014–15 season: NKL Round of 16
* 2015–16 season: NKL Quarterfinals
* 2016–17 season: NKL Third place
* 2017–18 season: NKL Third place

