'''Helsinki City Run''' is an annual [[half marathon]] that takes place every May as a [[road running]] event around the streets and parks of [[Helsinki]]. Starting in 1994{{r|history}} and organised by Suomen Urheiluliitto, the race has become popular over the years, attracting a record number of 17,000&nbsp;participants in 2013.{{r|2013 HS}}
